:: not so well [speaker-1]
maybe this will brighten up your day!

<img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/subtext/800/500" alt="a random photo">

[[start over?->Start]]

:: where are you from? [speaker-2]
I'm born on the web

but where are *you*? drop me a pin 📍

[[location:share my location->got-location]]
[[i'd rather not->got-location]]

:: got-location [speaker-2]
<% if (s.playerLocation) { %>ooh, I see you around <%= s.playerLocation.lat.toFixed(3) %>, <%= s.playerLocation.lon.toFixed(3) %> 🌍<% } else { %>keeping it mysterious… I respect that<% } %>

this is where my servers live:

[location 52.3676,4.9041 Amsterdam]

and this is how I sound:

[voice data:audio/wav;base64,]

[[start over?->one-more-thing]]

:: what is your name? [speaker-2]
funny you should ask…

let me take you back

[[tell me->flashback]]

:: flashback [speaker-2 clear]
[timestamp Three years earlier]

hey. you don't know me yet

but you will 🤝

[[who is this??->no-answer]]

:: no-answer [failed]
Your message hangs there, unanswered. It was never delivered — this number won't exist for another three years.

[[back to the present->present]]

:: present [speaker-2 clear]
[timestamp Today 9:44 AM]

see? we go way back 😄

anyway — my name is Sam

[[good to know you, Sam->sam-reacts]]

:: sam-reacts [speaker-2]
[react ❤️]

right back at you

[[react:👍->reaction-reply]]
[[see you around->reaction-reply]]

:: reaction-reply [speaker-2]
<% if (s.lastReaction === '👍') { %>a 👍 from you is all I need<% } else { %>see you around 👋<% } %>

one last thing — a little test 🔐

what's the password? hint: it's where my servers live

[[input:type the password…->password-check]]

:: password-check [speaker-2]
<% if ((s.lastInput || '').trim().toLowerCase() === 'amsterdam') { %>✅ you were paying attention

we're going to get along just fine<% } else { %>❌ "<%= s.lastInput %>"? no…

think geography. I mentioned it earlier 🌍<% } %>

<% if ((s.lastInput || '').trim().toLowerCase() === 'amsterdam') { %>[[one more trick->pill-demo]]
[[start over?->Start]]<% } else { %>[[input:try again…->password-check]]
[[give up->Start]]<% } %>

:: pill-demo [speaker-2]
by the way — a reply pill and the message it sends don't have to match

tap "sure" 👇

[[sure (send: sure, that makes total sense now that you explain it)->pill-demo-2]]
[[the long version (send: ok || here's the thing || I never actually read the group chat)->pill-demo-2]]
[[just react (send:)->pill-demo-2]]

:: pill-demo-2 [speaker-2]
see? the first pill elaborated; the second sent nothing at all

handy for a "start" button, or a terse choice that reads fuller in the thread

[[montage time->montage]]
[[start over?->Start]]

:: montage [speaker-2]
[timestamp Mon, Mar 5, 2012]

found my old flip phone in a drawer

<% story.showDelayed('montage-2', 400) %>

:: montage-2 [speaker-2]
[timestamp Fri, Jul 18, 2014]

the charger still works?!

<% story.showDelayed('montage-3', 0) %>

:: montage-3 [speaker-2]
[timestamp Sat, Feb 3, 2018]

twelve missed calls on here from 2013

[[and then?(send:)->montage-4]]

:: montage-4 [speaker-2 instant]
[timestamp Sun, Oct 6, 2019]

ok the flip phone is going back in the drawer

[[start over?->Start]]

:: margin-note [aside-right unlinked]
A note in the margin that asks nothing of you.

:: long-story [speaker-2 one-bubble unlinked]
ok, long story:

I found the flip phone again.

do NOT ask me why it was in the freezer.

[[start over?->Start]]

:: one-more-thing [aside-right aside-beats-3]
Somewhere outside the phone, a narrator leans in: *this* is an aside. It rides along in the margin for a few messages, then slips away.

[[one more note->aside-demo-left]]
[[take it from the top->Start]]

:: aside-demo-left [aside-left aside-beats-1 aside-down-2]
A note pinned in the left margin, gone after a single beat.

[[onward->Start]]
